      "title": "Man arrested for assaulting Welgama",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Another suspect has been arrested in connection with the assault on MP Kumara Welgama, the Police Media Spokesman's Office said.",
        "A 36 year old resident of Magammana, Homagama has been arrested.",
        "The suspect is running a small business and is due to be produced in court today, police said.",
        "The Police Media Spokesman's Office further states that 07 persons have been arrested in connection with the assault on Kumara Welgama."
      ],
